platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The Wizarding World springs to life in Harry Potter: Puzzles & Spells. Match your way through memorable momentsclearing puzzle boards of pesky trolls, chocolate frogs, and moreas youre treated to gorgeous levels inspired by the beloved books and films. This best-in-class match-3s most impressive bit of sorcery is conjuring up a distinct take on puzzle gamesone thats packed with spells, daily challenges, and collectible beasts. Youll feel as powerful as Dumbledore himself.
